<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0096b01"/><p id="pI01p0096b0101">大魏大統四年歲在戊
<lb ed="C I" n="0096b02"/>午十二月丙戊朔<note n="0096001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30506;＝辛【史】</note><app n="0096001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">辛</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30506;</rdg></app><note n="0096002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30636;＝亥【史】</note><app n="0096002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">亥</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30636;</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0096b03"/>日。佛弟子合邑卌人等。
<lb ed="C I" n="0096b04"/>生閻浮。運<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">遭</unclear>末劫。自飛
<lb ed="C I" n="0096b05"/>高因妙業。&CB07099;<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">以</unclear>同生彼
<lb ed="C I" n="0096b06"/><note n="0096003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30637;＝岸【史】</note><app n="0096003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">岸</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30637;</rdg></app>。遂尒<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">謫</unclear>相<note n="0096004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30638;＝率【史】</note><app n="0096004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">率</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30638;</rdg></app>化。<note n="0096005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30639;＝頃【史】</note><app n="0096005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">頃</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30639;</rdg></app>竭
<lb ed="C I" n="0096b07"/>己資。仰為皇帝國主。建
<lb ed="C I" n="0096b08"/>崇四面天宮石像一區。
<lb ed="C I" n="0096b09"/><note n="0096006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">逯＝逮【史】</note><app n="0096006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">逮</lem><rdg wit="【原】">逯</rdg></app>及師僧父母。七世所
<lb ed="C I" n="0096b10"/>生。因緣眷屬。香火邑義。
<lb ed="C I" n="0096b11"/>生〃世〃。值佛聞法。彌勒現
<lb ed="C I" n="0096b12"/>世。願登先首。<note n="0096007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30640;＝邊【史】</note><app n="0096007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30640;</rdg></app>地眾生。
<lb ed="C I" n="0096b13"/>普同正<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">覺</unclear>。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">咸</unclear>登正<note n="0096008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30641;＝果【史】</note><app n="0096008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">果</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30641;</rdg></app>。</p>
</div2>
